data.description: **Price reduction! Seller installing new roof** Built in 1971, the current owners purchased from the original owners! This home is located in the East Lake Park neighborhood where you have access to the boat ramp where you have access to the lake for boating, skiing and fishing! There are 2 bonus rooms off the master that can be used as an office or what ever you desire. The huge back yard also has a large shed for storage that will convey with the sale. This home is convienently located with easy access to I-4. With the Seminole Hardrock Hotel & Casino and Midflorida Amphitheatre just outside your front door this home is the ONE!
